"""
PART III Income

15. Income for the purposes of the Act

(1)

Editorial note: current text valid from 2025-03-21.

For the purposes of section 15(1)(e) (income), all social security benefits are prescribed except—

(e)

an increase of an allowance payable in respect of constant attendance under paragraph 4 of Part I of Schedule 8 to the 1992 Act;
"""

payment_is_social_security_benefit:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean

payment_is_increase_of_an_allowance:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean

allowance_is_payable_in_respect_of_constant_attendance:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean

allowance_is_under_paragraph_4_of_part_i_of_schedule_8_to_the_1992_act:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean

allowance_is_payable_in_respect_of_constant_attendance_under_paragraph_4_of_part_i_of_schedule_8_to_the_1992_act:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean
    from 2025-03-21:
        allowance_is_payable_in_respect_of_constant_attendance and allowance_is_under_paragraph_4_of_part_i_of_schedule_8_to_the_1992_act

constant_attendance_allowance_increase_is_excepted_from_prescribed_benefits_15_1_e:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean
    from 2025-03-21:
        payment_is_social_security_benefit and payment_is_increase_of_an_allowance and allowance_is_payable_in_respect_of_constant_attendance_under_paragraph_4_of_part_i_of_schedule_8_to_the_1992_act
